---
title: Creamy Double Butter Chicken Filo Pie with Roasted Veggies
description: We’re taking the crowd favourite creamy, mild Indian-style spiced butter chicken and wrapping it in golden filo pastry. What does
this get us? One delicious pie that’s for sure! With the added flavour of roasted veggies tossed in, you’re really in for a good time.
